name: interactive #008 // starhunter - lost signal
description:
interactive real-time flight experience. starhunter's hyperdrive landed you in the wrong celestial coordinates, nothing left to do but to explore...

keyboard controls: 
* [WASD] movement
* [SPACE/T] up+down
* [E] hyperpulse
* [V] toggle cockpit

a collab between @eddietree and @ktk

NOTE: this functionality relies on the hicdex API -- changes in the API may affect experience. developed in threejs
